'SELECT DISTINCT TO_CHAR(SYSDATE,''YYYY-MM-DD'') AS CHAR_DATE, A.CUSTOM_ID, C.DATE, CASE WHEN B.VALUE1 IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE
(ROUND(B.VALUE1 / 1024 / 1024)) END AS DL_TOTAL_30D,

FROM TOTAL.V_TOTAL_PROFILE as A
LEFT JOIN TOTAL.V_TOTAL_PROFILE as B ON A.ID = B.ID
LEFT JOIN TOTAL.V_TOTAL_EQUIPMENT as C ON to_number(A.VALUE) = C.VALUE

WHERE 1=1 AND ((A.TYPE = ''GOLD'') OR (A.TYPE = ''SILVER'' AND A.AGE > 10)) AND A.IS_RUNNING = 1 AND A.CUSTOMER_ID IS NOT NULL

SELECT DISTINCT u.id, SELECT(
    SELECT * FROM user_data WHERE id = 1
) as data FROM user as u WHERE u.id = 1 LAST u.id'

'SELECT DISTINCT
TO_CHAR(SYSDATE,''YYYY-MM-DD'') AS CHAR_DATE,
A.CUSTOM_ID,
A.SYSDATE_WE,
A.SYSDATE,
A.ROUND,
A.SELECT,

FROM TEST AS A
